transcript.content: Good afternoon. LAMA GP surgery. How can I assist you in your emergency?
Hi, I need urgent help. I am experiencing heart attack symptoms.
Can you confirm your name and date of birth for identity verification?
My name is Jennifer Wilcox and I was born on April 23, 1999.
Thank you, Jennifer Wilcox. I've located your records. Let me assist you immediately.
Please stay calm. I am arranging an ambulance for your heart attack symptoms. Is there someone with you?
Good. Ensure they keep you comfortable. The ambulance will arrive shortly. Please stay on the line for any updates.
